app_details.title: Injector Origin
app_details.description: Injector Origin is more than just an injector app. Dive into our hero guides, packed with valuable tips and tricks to master every hero's abilities and strategies. Elevate your skills and enhance your gaming experience with Injector Origin now!

reviews.content: The ads are easy to skip and with fast injection
reviews.replyContent: Thanks for your feedback! We're happy to hear that you find the ads easy to skip and enjoy the fast injection. We’re committed to providing a smooth experience, so stay tuned for more updates!
Thank you! We're glad to hear you think it's one of the better injectors. We'll keep working hard to make it even better for you!

reviews.content: the steps is hard but it's good
reviews.replyContent: Thanks for your feedback! We’re glad you think it’s good, though we understand the steps might seem a bit tricky. We’ll work on making things easier in future updates to improve your experience!

reviews.content: This was GREAT! It had a lot of new skins but the problem is that there are a lot of bugs like fredrinn neo beast with the default voice and ui. And can you guys please add custom skins/anime skins that would be great 👍
reviews.replyContent: Thanks for your feedback! We're glad you enjoyed the new skins. Regarding the bugs, we’re aware that some of the voicelines, like Fredrinn Neo Beast, don’t work anymore, and we’re working on fixing them. As for custom and anime skins, we’re exploring adding those in the future, so stay tuned for more updates!
